channel.title: My First Trace - Proving 14-08 Wrong
channel.description:
Well, since 14-08 doesnt think i can trace well, heres my way of proving him wrong. here is the origional: [img]http://thumbs.dreamstime.com/thumb_232/1201880115h44MJV.jpg[/img]
and heres mine (High Poly) [IMG]http://i369.photobucket.com/albums/oo131/0xXDylanXx0/trace.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i369.photobucket.com/albums/oo131/0xXDylanXx0/high2.jpg[/img]
(Low Poly) - rs capable [IMG]http://i369.photobucket.com/albums/oo131/0xXDylanXx0/low-1.jpg[/img] what appears to be glitched faces is just a mix of texture errors and conversion of high-low poly. sorry, no 2nd screenshot, blender kept freezing.
If thats not enough, i have a 45min hypercam vid of me making it.

item.title: My First Trace - Proving 14-08 Wrong
item.dc:creator: @dylan_0789 dylan_0789
item.description:
@dylan_0789 wrote:

14-08:

[quote]I misread you, i thought you wanted me to make it the same, not better. High-poly’s only diff was in the blade, i didnt round off the hilt/handle, i could always make the v1.2 with it fully high-poly and better than the origional.

Dylan, I am sorry if offended you in any way. I just get insulted surprisingly easily. By the way, I never said you can’t trace, I said I didn’t think anyone can trace and make it look better than the original. But, I take it back. To be honest, yours looks as good if not better than the original. There are a few things you could change to perhaps make it look better. But, this isn’t one of your good models, right? you just made it quickly to prove me wrong?

Anyways, I do apologize, I honestly didn’t mean to offend you.

 ~~ 14-08[/quote]

tbh this is one of my rushed models. i made it fast to show i could trace. if i put time into it i could have done serious improvements, noticing the flaws of the origional image

But still, a lot better than mine
